---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy notice · Blackfen Little Learners">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container-prose">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Privacy notice</p>
      <h1 class="text-balance">How we handle your information.</h1>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-ink-700/85">
        <p>
          This is a placeholder privacy notice. Before going live, this page
          should be reviewed against current UK GDPR / Data Protection Act
          guidance — for childminders the ICO's small-business guidance is a
          good starting point.
        </p>

        <h3>Who we are</h3>
        <p>
          Blackfen Little Learners is a registered childminding setting
          operating in Blackfen, Greater London. For the purposes of UK
          GDPR, the childminder is the data controller for the personal
          information described below.
        </p>

        <h3>What we collect</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Contact details you provide via the enquiry form (name, email, message).</li>
          <li>Information about your child once a place is offered (name, date of birth, dietary needs, emergency contacts, medical information).</li>
          <li>Records of attendance, observations, and learning journeys, as required by the EYFS framework.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>How we use it</h3>
        <p>
          To respond to your enquiry, to provide childcare, to meet our
          obligations under the EYFS framework and Ofsted registration, and
          to keep your child safe.
        </p>

        <h3>How long we keep it</h3>
        <p>
          Enquiries that don't lead to a placement are deleted within 6
          months. Records relating to children in our care are kept in
          accordance with statutory requirements.
        </p>

        <h3>Your rights</h3>
        <p>
          You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your
          personal information, and to complain to the ICO. To exercise any
          of these rights, please get in touch.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm text-ink-700/60">
          Last updated: placeholder.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
